function lunchPopup(modalContent){

var modal = $('#modalMessage');
modal.find('.modal-footer').html('');

$.each(modalContent.buttons, function(index, value) {
var callback = "";
if(value.calback != ""){
callback = "onclick=\""+value.calback+"\"";
}

if(value.link != "" && typeof value.link != 'undefined'){
callback = "onclick=\"gotto('"+value.link+"');\"";
//callback = "onclick=\"alert('toto');\"";
}

var addbutton = "<button "+callback+" type=\"button\" class=\"btn "+value.btntype+"\" data-dismiss=\"modal\">"+value.text+"</button>";
modal.find('.modal-footer').append(addbutton);
});

if (typeof modalContent.content[0].class != 'undefined'){
var modalclass = modalContent.content[0].class;
modal.addClass(modalclass);
}

modal.find('.modal-title').html(modalContent.content[0].title);
modal.find('.modal-body').html(modalContent.content[0].body);
